<a class="title" href="/nodes/95985/comments/1398325">Re: Quelques avis en passant</a>
</h2>
<p class="meta">
Posté par <a href="/users/kliger" rel="author">Polo</a> <time class="updated" datetime="2012-10-14T09:26:35+02:00"><span class="date">le 14/10/12</span> <span class="time">à 09:26</span></time>.
